{"tid":1586020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10月1日 <保衛香港之全面地區戰>","createTime":"2019-09-21T18:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T14:41:43.000Z","uid":289747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"38e8c5c4c2f7c760e733c46e195ee34e3188149f","tid":1586020,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:40:14.000Z","msg":"1. 黨鐵到時候必定全線封站。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 全面地區戰目的在於分散狗力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 手足對自己附近嘅地區會比較熟悉地形同路線，知己知彼，自然得心應手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 必須各區起義！唔好集中一兩個區！當然人多就固然好，但人多嘅時候，狗畜就易於管理我哋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />徹退果陣又混亂又慢又無路走，變相或多或少都有手足送頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 有清晰目標(eg. 黨鐵站/建制狗辦事處/狗屋)，全力徹底攻擊摧毀完，返屋企瞓覺，途中順便獅鳥藍屍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 有人話如果全面地區戰嘅話，唔知每區手足人數會有幾多，分薄狗畜嘅同時，分薄埋自己。我想講，8.5 果日我哋都得，唔係10.1 唔得呀嘛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37b831a8fd5377115c2f16113e40f62090dabea","tid":1586020,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc96a3ae5548c375db85493d5edd7825be820ff","tid":1586020,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:40:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8ef30be41a9741759830cf07de1da4fd225866b","tid":1586020,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a7440e0f12ad6f7488e6dc852ae16c2a9fd74a","tid":1586020,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:41:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57f75c2b0813ee60b1f04816333bdd78da3a3ba","tid":1586020,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfc96a3ae5548c375db85493d5edd7825be820ff","tid":1586020,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:40:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:46:38.000Z","msg":"所以我話私了唔係一個清晰嘅攻擊目標，而係順個便，班藍屍唔搞我哋，唔多口多手，我哋自然返屋企瞓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005f05ab3943740f45afbdd45910a0163b096401","tid":1586020,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:50:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">哂佢冷</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmo